b'With the Whirlpool:registered: App, keeping your laundry moving while you\xe2\x80\x99re on-the-go will become a little easier. You\xe2\x80\x99ll be able to monitor your load, order detergent, or even use the Task Manager to assign tasks to your family members like starting the washer or folding the clothes, right from your phone. #ces2019 #ConnectToMore \nDetails and privacy info at whirlpool.com/connect.'
b'No need to transfer clothes from the washer to the dryer. The Whirlpool:registered: Smart All-In-One Washer and Dryer lets you do your laundry in fewer steps.\n#CES2019 #ConnectToMore'

b'The Whirlpool Connected Hub Wall Oven, an exciting new concept from WLabs:trade_mark:, will take you step by step through recipes on its LCD screen, so you can have peace of mind that every dish will reach your table just as it should, and at the right time. #CES2019 #ConnectToMore'

b'You can\xe2\x80\x99t skip washing the sheets, the towels, the blankets and the pillows. But now you can skip adding detergent to every load. Whirlpool\xe2\x93\x87 Load & Go:trade_mark: dispenser holds up to 40 loads of detergent. #CES2019 #ConnectToMore\n\nAvailable on select Whirlpool:registered: models. Loads are 8lbs.'

b'We\xe2\x80\x99re excited to preview the Connected Hub Wall Oven. Its LCD touch screen tells you when your whole family is free to eat together all while guiding you through tonight\xe2\x80\x99s dinner recipe, so every night can be family night. #CES2019 #ConnectToMore'

b'Life doesn\xe2\x80\x99t stop for laundry. That\xe2\x80\x99s why the Whirlpool:registered: app will soon be able to connect with your Apple Watch:registered: to send you updates so you can control your laundry from anywhere.\n#CES2019 #ConnectToMore'

b'There\xe2\x80\x99s a new family member here to help around the house: the Whirlpool:registered: App. Coming soon, just sync with your compatible voice-enabled device to start, stop, check and change your laundry cycle on select smart appliances. #CES2019 #ConnectToMore\n\nDetails and privacy info at whirlpool.com/connect. Appliance must be set to Remote Enable.'

b'The term \xe2\x80\x9ceasy as pie\xe2\x80\x9d has never meant more. b'Sometimes mustard gets on more than just your sandwich. b'Whirlpool works with @Yummly to recognize the ingredients you have on hand, help you plan meals for the week ahead, and instantly order missing ingredients right to your door! #CES2019 #ConnectToMore\n\nLearn more in the Yummly:registered: app. Grocery delivery may vary by location.'
